data.description: 15 +/- Acre MINI FARM!  You do not want to miss this FULL BRICK BASEMENT RANCH Home featuring 3 Bedrooms, 3 Full Bathrooms, MOUNTAIN VIEWS with a BARN!  What more can you ask for?  With almost 2,000 square foot of road frontage, you will enjoy privacy with a fenced pasture, year round stream, 2 stall barn with tack room and hay storage.  The interior is designed with hardwood floors, Andersen windows, Enclosed back porch and granite counter tops. All of this on a full finished walk out basement!  Call or text for your private showing today!
